top.parak.kraft.core.log.sequence

类 AbstractEntrySequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • top.parak.kraft.core.log.sequence.AbstractEntrySequence
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    EntrySequence
    直接已知子类:
    FileEntrySequence, MemoryEntrySequence

    @NotThreadSafe
public abstract class AbstractEntrySequence
extends Object
implements EntrySequence
    Abstract entry sequence.

    Structure of entry sequence

     +-----------+-----------+-----------+-----------+- - - - - -+
 |   entry   |   entry   |   entry   |   entry   |   entry   |
 +-----------+-----------+-----------+-----------+- - - - - -+
       ↑                                   ↑           ↑
 logIndexOffset(firstLogIndex)        lastLogIndex nextLogIndex
    从以下版本开始:
    2022-04-01
    作者:
    KHighness
